Flow is a static type checker for JavaScript. This is a list of Flow types generated from the source code in https://github.com/facebook/flow/tree/v0.47.0/ The script to generate this list is on github. Fixes welcome.

  • There are separate sections for "private" or "magic" types with a $ in the name. See the note here and comment here. Update: Some these types are now documented here.
  • Links in bold point to the Flow documentation. Other links point to the Flow source code.

Built-in "private" types

  • $Abstract
  • $All<...T> is the intersection of types ...T
  • $Diff<A, B>
  • $Either<...T> is the union of types ...T
  • $Exact<T>
  • $Exports<'M'> is the type of the exports of module 'M'
  • $Keys<T>
  • $NonMaybeType<T> acts as the type T without null and void
  • $ObjMap<T, F>
  • $Pred
  • $PropertyType<T, k>
  • $Refine
  • $Shape<T> matches the shape of T
  • $Subtype<T> acts as any over subtypes of T
  • $Supertype<T> acts as any over supertypes of T
  • $Tainted
  • $TupleMap<T, F>
  • $Type<T> acts as the type of T
